<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_199_r1l15"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_199_r1l16"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / daʒ vvir die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l17">Lancʒhüt <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllen / So wöllet Jr Jn hilfflich ſein / daʒ ſie 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">güte die Jn ſchuldig ſein </del> <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchuld <expan>beköme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_199_r1l18">vnd becʒalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab></add> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> güt die Jn ſchuldıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l20">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>we<ex>r</ex>n</expan></del> / ſein / wo ſie <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> abgank daran <expan>gewünne<ex>n</ex></expan> / das wöllet Jr Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l21">auf <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> güt <expan>erſtatt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd da für ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l22">die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ſind beſant vnd ſie <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l23">hören / Nu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteet</expan> ewr gnad wol / daʒ Jn nicht füglich <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l24">ſich Jr <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> / dheins <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gütes der Jm nicht ſchuldig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l25"><expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>wünd</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> einnem / Davon <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> vnd getrawen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l26">
<del rend="strikethrough">wölle </del> wol / daʒ Jr ſchıcken wöllet / daʒ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchulde ſüſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_199_r1l27">entrichtet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_199" id="99r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, daz wir die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen Lanczhüt
                            <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> süllen, so wöllet ir in hilfflich sein,
                        daz sie <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> schuld <expan>beköme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>und beczalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan></add>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> güt, die in schuldig sein; wo sie
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> abgank daran
                            <expan>gewünne<ex>n</ex></expan>, das wöllet ir in auf
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> güt <expan>erstatt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        dafür ein<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir die
                        <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim sind,
                        besant und sie <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief lassen hören. Nu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steet</expan> ewr gnad wol, daz in nicht füglich
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz sich ir
                            <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> dheins <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        gütes, der im nicht schuldig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>,
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>wünd</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> einnem. Davon <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>
                        und getrawen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, daz ir schicken wöllet, daz die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> schulde süst entrichtet
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
